  "Description": [
    "Sphinx extension to document classes with Traitlets-based config This is a Sphinx extension that builds on sphinx.ext.autodoc to better document classes with Traitlets-based configuration.  It provides Sphinx directives `autoconfigurable` (use with classes) and `autotrait` (use with the traitlets based configuration options), yielding documentation that takes account of Traitlets."
